<br>
The key is to prevent abuse of double booking, so if a guild wanted to invite a huge number from non-rotation guilds it dosen't really matter.  (Even if they cannot do it /wo those invites, but can invite enough guys to be consistently able to kill sev, then nothing is lost.)<br>
